":"騰訊大股東"},{"pid":"1c9e444bf83c69604ce5ee8e4833b463d5f82fb9","tid":2452473,"uid":62073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJhDaXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJhDaXD.jpg&h=c8a592bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca9cfb266b5eb0ffe43c3acaad2ad9eb016ebc1f","tid":2452473,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826a98cf5659b56bccf19d7d4bc0006be8dd07f5","tid":2452473,"uid":62073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"抽聯易融<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2454049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2454049/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7da84b5cd0f5eda92f37769e79af007912939ec6","tid":2452473,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4af53201bf25a75be8557ecab4a402fe8954954","tid":2452473,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"HSBC<br />\n<br />\n是次貸款年利率為:<br />\n<br />\n- 新股認購貸款金額高於港幣300萬：年息0.90%<br />\n- 新股認購貸款金額等於或低於港幣300萬：年息1.10%<br />\n<br />\n新股認購貸款截止申請時間：2021年3月23日19:00 (下午7時正) 或總申請貸款金額已達到本行指定之最高貸款限額。<br />\n<br />\n-只接受以個人名義滙豐卓越理財，滙豐One或個人綜合理財客户;<br />\n-每一個貸款申請最低貸款額為港幣10萬元;<br />\n-是次新股認購最高貸款金額為港幣2,000萬;<br />\n-每個客户最高總貸款金額為港幣3,000萬，包括同期所有新股認購貸款;<br />\n-須有香港住址登記於本行記錄。<br />\n<br />\n如果您想利用新股認購貸款服務認購新股，請注意有關新股認購及貸款申請必須同時遞交。"},{"pid":"ae768e0d0a15d9dc050603047a15c725b3aa750e","tid":2452473,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"6608 冇人玩？"},{"pid":"477ec4bb8315c679c2f33ebe48a97d64436a26b0","tid":2452473,"uid":210001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy